{"an11.1:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 11.1 ","an11.1:0.2":"1. Nissayavagga ","an11.1:0.3":"Kimatthiyasutta ","an11.1:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","an11.1:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","an11.1:1.3":"Atha kho ayasma anando yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam nisidi. Ekamantam nisinno kho ayasma anando bhagavantam etadavoca: ","an11.1:1.4":"“kimatthiyani, bhante, kusalani silani kimanisamsani”ti? ","an11.1:1.5":"“Avippatisaratthani kho, ananda, kusalani silani avippatisaranisamsani”ti. ","an11.1:2.1":"“Avippatisaro pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimanisamso”? ","an11.1:2.2":"“Avippatisaro kho, ananda, pamojjattho pamojjanisamso”. ","an11.1:3.1":"“Pamojjam pana, bhante, kimatthiyam kimanisamsam”? ","an11.1:3.2":"“Pamojjam kho, ananda, pitattham pitanisamsam”. ","an11.1:4.1":"“Piti pana, bhante, kimatthiya kimanisamsa”? ","an11.1:4.2":"“Piti kho, ananda, passaddhattha passaddhanisamsa”. ","an11.1:5.1":"“Passaddhi pana, bhante, kimatthiya kimanisamsa”? ","an11.1:5.2":"“Passaddhi kho, ananda, sukhattha sukhanisamsa”. ","an11.1:6.1":"“Sukham pana, bhante, kimatthiyam kimanisamsam”? ","an11.1:6.2":"“Sukham kho, ananda, samadhattham samadhanisamsam”. ","an11.1:7.1":"“Samadhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimanisamso”? ","an11.1:7.2":"“Samadhi kho, ananda, yathabhutananadassanattho yathabhutananadassananisamso”. ","an11.1:8.1":"“Yathabhutananadassanam pana, bhante, kimatthiyam kimanisamsam”? ","an11.1:8.2":"“Yathabhutananadassanam kho, ananda, nibbidattham nibbidanisamsam”. ","an11.1:9.1":"“Nibbida pana, bhante, kimatthiya kimanisamsa”? ","an11.1:9.2":"“Nibbida kho, ananda, viragattha viraganisamsa”. ","an11.1:10.1":"“Virago pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimanisamso”? ","an11.1:10.2":"“Virago kho, ananda, vimuttinanadassanattho vimuttinanadassananisamso. ","an11.1:11.1":"Iti kho, ananda, kusalani silani avippatisaratthani avippatisaranisamsani, ","an11.1:11.2":"avippatisaro pamojjattho pamojjanisamso, ","an11.1:11.3":"pamojjam pitattham pitanisamsam, ","an11.1:11.4":"piti passaddhattha passaddhanisamsa, ","an11.1:11.5":"passaddhi sukhattha sukhanisamsa, ","an11.1:11.6":"sukham samadhattham samadhanisamsam, ","an11.1:11.7":"samadhi yathabhutananadassanattho yathabhutananadassananisamso, ","an11.1:11.8":"yathabhutananadassanam nibbidattham nibbidanisamsam, ","an11.1:11.9":"nibbida viragattha viraganisamsa, ","an11.1:11.10":"virago vimuttinanadassanattho vimuttinanadassananisamso. ","an11.1:11.11":"Iti kho, ananda, kusalani silani anupubbena aggaya parenti”ti. ","an11.1:11.12":"Pathamam. "}